Sial.

34
00:04:17,382 --> 00:04:18,466
Napas Air.

35
00:04:19,050 --> 00:04:20,927
Jurus Kedua Terbaru.

36
00:04:21,803 --> 00:04:23,429
Kincir Air Lateral.

37
00:04:44,575 --> 00:04:45,743
Apa-apaan ini?

38
