<i>Aku tak boleh menyerah.</i>

70
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:46,424
<i>Siapa kau?</i>

71
00:07:50,553 --> 00:07:51,971
Halo.

72
00:07:52,555 --> 00:07:54,098
Kau baik-baik saja?

73
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:03,232
Napas Air. Jurus Kedua.

74
00:08:04,859 --> 00:08:06,277
Kincir Air!

75
00:08:13,951 --> 00:08:15,912
Aku bisa mendarat dengan selamat.

76
00:08:19,373 --> 00:08:21,292
Kumohon. Tolong hentikan!

77
00:08:51,197 --> 00:08:52,740
Kau lihat apa?

78
00:08:53,533 --> 00:08:55,618
Tidak ada yang bisa dilihat di sini.

79
00:08:58,204 --> 00:08:59,622
Apa yang kau lakukan?

80
00:09:00,373 --> 00:09:03,084
Bukankah kalian rekan?

81
00:09:03,834 --> 00:09:05,044
Rekan?

82
00:09:05,711 --> 00:09:08,714
Jangan satukan kami
dengan hubungan rapuh macam itu.

83
00:09:09,298 --> 00:09:11,092
Kami keluarga.

84
00:09:11,676 --> 00:09:14,136
Ada ikatan kuat di antara kami.

85
00:09:15,137 --> 00:09:16,764
Belum lagi,

86
00:09:17,431 --> 00:09:19,725
ini masalahku dengan kakakku.

87
00:09:20,643 --> 00:09:22,728
Jika kau ikut campur,

88
00:09:23,604 --> 00:09:24,855
aku akan memotongmu.

89
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,442
Itu tidak benar.

90
00:09:28,776 --> 00:09:30,361
Entah itu keluargamu atau rekan,

91
00:09:30,695 --> 00:09:32,697
jika ada ikatan kuat
antara satu sama lain,

92
00:09:32,905 --> 00:09:34,740
kalian berharga bagi satu sama lain.

93
00:09:35,533 --> 00:09:38,077
Hanya karena tak ada hubungan darah,
kau bilang itu rapuh.

94
00:09:38,661 --> 00:09:40,037
Itu tak benar!

95
00:09:40,746 --> 00:09:44,166
Jika kalian terhubung dengan ikatan kuat,

96
00:09:44,250 --> 00:09:45,751
aku bisa mencium kepercayaan.

97
00:09:46,252 --> 00:09:47,920
Tapi aku hanya bisa mencium

98
00:09:48,337 --> 00:09:51,090
rasa takut, kebencian,
dan teror dari kalian berdua.

99
00:09:51,882 --> 00:09:54,093
Itu bukan ikatan.

100
00:09:54,427 --> 00:09:55,636
Ini palsu.

101
00:09:55,928 --> 00:09:57,221
Ikatan palsu!

102
00:10:03,060 --> 00:10:04,395
Kau...

103
00:10:10,651 --> 00:10:13,362
Tampaknya ada iblis
berukuran tepat di sini.

104
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:17,450
Bahkan aku bisa menangani
anak iblis seperti ini.

105
00:10:18,701 --> 00:10:21,370
- Tunggu...
- Sebaiknya kau menyingkir.

106
00:10:21,746 --> 00:10:24,332
Aku mau mengambil batu loncatan yang aman.

107
00:10:24,999 --> 00:10:29,211
Selama kau bisa naik,
ganjaran yang diberikan akan meningkat.

108
00:10:29,670 --> 00:10:32,882
Hampir semua anggota timku tewas.

109
00:10:32,965 --> 00:10:36,510
Aku harus mengalahkan
iblis bertubuh sedang

110
00:10:36,594 --> 00:10:38,012
sebelum aku turun gunung.

111
00:10:38,638 --> 00:10:39,555
Majulah!

112
00:10:39,639 --> 00:10:41,223
Jangan, hentikan!

113
00:10:47,813 --> 00:10:49,899
<i>Dia memotongnya begitu saja.</i>

114
00:10:50,358 --> 00:10:51,567
<i>Apa yang terjadi?</i>

115
00:10:52,902 --> 00:10:55,321
Hei, kau bilang apa tadi?

116
00:11:00,201 --> 00:11:01,327
Kau...

117
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:04,997
Kau tadi bilang apa?

118
00:11:08,084 --> 00:11:09,835
<i>Sensasi yang sangat menegangkan.</i>

119
00:11:10,628 --> 00:11:13,923
<i>Udara terasa sangat berat dan dingin.</i>

120
00:11:16,675 --> 00:11:18,803
<i>Maaf, Inosuke.</i>

121
00:11:19,553 --> 00:11:22,306
<i>Lakukan yang terbaik dan bertahanlah.</i>

122
00:11:23,015 --> 00:11:25,601
<i>Setelah kukalahkan iblis ini,
aku akan mencarimu.</i>

123
00:11:27,144 --> 00:11:29,772
<i>Aku pasti akan menyelamatkanmu.</i>

124
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:33,609
Perkataanmu tadi.

125
00:11:34,777 --> 00:11:36,654
Coba ulangi.

126
00:11:38,197 --> 00:11:39,156
Hei.

127
00:11:39,698 --> 00:11:41,158
Katakanlah.

128
00:11:41,742 --> 00:11:44,286
Tentu. Aku akan mengulanginya
sebanyak yang kau mau.

129
00:11:44,787 --> 00:11:46,956
Ikatan kalian palsu!

130
00:12:14,024 --> 00:12:15,234
<i>Gawat.</i>

131
00:12:30,324 --> 00:12:31,325
<i>Sial.</i>

132
00:12:31,659 --> 00:12:33,911
<i>Aku bersembunyi di tempat seperti ini.</i>

133
00:12:33,995 --> 00:12:35,496
<i>Dasar pengecut.</i>

134
00:12:36,247 --> 00:12:38,458
<i>Tapi aku harus memikirkannya baik-baik.</i>

135
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:42,336
<i>Apa cara terbaik menembus kulit iblis
yang tak bisa ditembus?</i>

136
00:12:43,254 --> 00:12:45,923
<i>Apa yang harus kulakukan?</i>

137
00:12:46,215 --> 00:12:48,718
<i>Apa yang harus kulakukan
untuk menembus kulitnya?</i>

138
00:12:49,177 --> 00:12:52,221
<i>Pikirkan!</i>

139
00:12:57,477 --> 00:12:59,687
<i>Gawat, ini gawat!</i>

140
00:13:00,605 --> 00:13:01,772
<i>Sebelum bocah itu...</i>

141
00:13:01,856 --> 00:13:05,359
<i>Sebelum bocah itu kembali,
aku harus mencari cara.</i>

142
00:13:08,237 --> 00:13:10,656
Pola pikir bodoh macam apa ini?

143
00:13:12,825 --> 00:13:15,411
Kau bercanda?

144
00:13:21,959 --> 00:13:23,878
Sialan kau.

145
00:13:24,879 --> 00:13:29,050
Aku terkontaminasi bakteri Tontaro.

146
00:13:29,133 --> 00:13:30,968
Aku jadi berpikir seperti dia.

147
00:13:31,052 --> 00:13:32,929
Hampir saja aku terpengaruh.

148
00:13:33,346 --> 00:13:38,059
<i>Berpikir tak mencerminkan sifat asliku!</i>

149
00:13:42,438 --> 00:13:45,149
Bagaimana? Kupotong tanganmu!

150
00:13:47,026 --> 00:13:49,153
Semudah itu.

151
00:13:49,278 --> 00:13:51,113
Jika tak bisa kupotong sekali tebas,

152
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:54,575
kuhantam saja pedangnya sampai menembus.

153
00:13:54,867 --> 00:13:58,871
Karena aku punya dua pedang!

154
00:14:01,457 --> 00:14:03,376
Aku yang terkuat!

155
00:14:08,798 --> 00:14:10,800
Kenapa kau melarikan diri?

156
00:14:11,050 --> 00:14:13,844
Tunggu, Berengsek!

157
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:28,818
Biar kujelaskan dahulu.

158
00:14:29,068 --> 00:14:31,988
Aku takkan langsung membunuhmu.

159
00:14:32,572 --> 00:14:35,992
Aku akan memotong dan mencincangmu.

160
00:14:40,162 --> 00:14:41,205
Namun,

161
00:14:41,706 --> 00:14:44,041
jika kau menarik kembali kata-katamu,

162
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:46,711
aku akan mengampunimu
dan langsung membunuhmu.

163
00:14:46,961 --> 00:14:48,254
Takkan kutarik ucapanku!

164
00:14:48,671 --> 00:14:50,756
Semua perkataanku benar!

165
00:14:51,507 --> 00:14:54,260
Kaulah masalahnya!

166
00:15:01,517 --> 00:15:03,853
Kau yang salah!

167
00:15:20,912 --> 00:15:21,871
<i>Sial.</i>

168
00:15:21,954 --> 00:15:25,499
<i>Ke mana dia pergi? Sial.</i>

169
00:15:28,961 --> 00:15:32,298
Cedera ini tak sakit sama sekali.

170
00:15:32,673 --> 00:15:35,509
Aku sama sekali tak merasa sakit.

171
00:15:35,927 --> 00:15:37,094
Karena sudah begini,

172
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:39,680
aku harus menemukannya.

173
00:15:51,859 --> 00:15:53,277
Di sana kau rupanya!

174
00:15:53,778 --> 00:15:57,365
Kenapa bedebah ini memanjat setinggi itu?

175
00:15:58,574 --> 00:15:59,784
Berengsek!

176
00:15:59,992 --> 00:16:03,371
Dia memainkan trik
untuk membuatku berpikir.

177
00:16:03,871 --> 00:16:05,289
Aku takkan tertipu.

178
00:16:09,502 --> 00:16:10,503
Apa?

179
00:16:11,253 --> 00:16:12,713
Begitu rupanya.

180
00:16:13,047 --> 00:16:16,467
Kau gemetar ketakutan karena aku.

181
00:16:18,511 --> 00:16:20,304
Sudah terlambat sekarang!

182
00:16:26,060 --> 00:16:27,979
Apa? Ini...

183
00:16:33,275 --> 00:16:35,695
Dia melepas kulitnya!

184
00:16:46,789 --> 00:16:47,915
<i>Tak mungkin.</i>

185
00:16:48,290 --> 00:16:51,585
<i>Bagaimana bisa jadi begitu besar?</i>

186
00:16:52,086 --> 00:16:53,629
<i>Ini gawat.</i>

187
00:16:54,296 --> 00:16:58,259
<i>Aku belum pernah merasakan
tekanan sebesar ini dari musuh.</i>

188
00:16:58,968 --> 00:17:01,137
<i>Tekanannya saja sudah membuatku hancur.</i>

189
00:17:06,517 --> 00:17:07,601
<i>Habislah aku.</i>

190
00:17:08,185 --> 00:17:09,228
<i>Aku tak bisa menang.</i>

191
00:17:17,194 --> 00:17:18,446
<i>Aku akan mati.</i>

192
00:17:20,364 --> 00:17:21,657
<i>Dia akan membunuhku.</i>

193
00:17:23,034 --> 00:17:24,035
<i>Jangan mati!</i>

194
00:17:25,494 --> 00:17:28,122
Sebelum aku kembali, jangan mati!

195
00:17:29,415 --> 00:17:34,628
<i>Kalian harus bangga pada diri kalian
dan terus berusaha bertahan hidup.</i>

196
00:17:35,337 --> 00:17:37,298
<i>Semoga perjuangan kalian lancar.</i>

197
00:17:40,134 --> 00:17:41,260
Aku takkan menyerah!

198
00:17:42,636 --> 00:17:44,638
Aku takkan pernah menyerah!

199
00:17:45,556 --> 00:17:49,268
Aku Inosuke Hashibira
dari Korps Pembasmi Iblis.

200
00:17:49,393 --> 00:17:52,104
Majulah, Berengsek!

201
00:17:53,981 --> 00:17:54,940
<i>Dia cepat.</i>

202
00:17:55,149 --> 00:17:56,358
<i>Aku tak bisa melihatnya.</i>

203
00:18:03,074 --> 00:18:04,909
Napas Hewan Buas.

204
00:18:05,701 --> 00:18:07,078
Taring Ketiga.

205
00:18:07,453 --> 00:18:08,954
Koyak dan Telan.

206
00:18:10,998 --> 00:18:11,957
Apa?

207
00:18:17,463 --> 00:18:18,631
<i>Sial.</i>

208
00:18:19,006 --> 00:18:21,842
<i>Aku tak sempat menyesuaikan
dan diserang sebab Gaya Bernapasku.</i>

209
00:18:23,177 --> 00:18:27,515
Menjauhlah dari keluargaku.

210
00:18:28,432 --> 00:18:30,392
<i>Aku takkan mati.</i>

211
00:18:30,893 --> 00:18:33,771
<i>Napas Hewan Buas. Taring Pertama.</i>

212
00:18:34,814 --> 00:18:37,650
<i>Terima ini. Tusukan Menembus!</i>

213
00:18:39,944 --> 00:18:41,320
<i>Masuk.</i>

214
00:18:41,529 --> 00:18:43,197
<i>Meskipun aku menusuknya,</i>

215
00:18:43,572 --> 00:18:47,326
<i>sepertinya dia tak merasakan apa pun.</i>

216
00:19:07,763 --> 00:19:09,056
Maafkan aku.

217
00:19:11,684 --> 00:19:14,228
Maaf, Inosuke.

218
00:19:26,824 --> 00:19:28,826
Kau harus tetap hidup.

219
00:19:29,785 --> 00:19:30,953
Inosuke.

220
00:19:37,835 --> 00:19:40,963
Siapa itu?

221
00:19:52,141 --> 00:19:53,350
<i>Apa yang terjadi?</i>

222
00:19:55,311 --> 00:19:57,897
<i>Diakah yang melakukannya?</i>

223
00:19:59,148 --> 00:20:02,860
<i>Siapa dia?</i>

224
00:20:14,330 --> 00:20:15,331
<i>Cepat sekali.</i>

225
00:20:17,124 --> 00:20:19,793
<i>Napas Air. Jurus Keempat.</i>

226
00:20:20,211 --> 00:20:21,170
<i>Gelombang Pemecah.</i>

227
00:20:29,803 --> 00:20:32,181
<i>Hebat sekali.</i>

228
00:20:37,311 --> 00:20:40,272
<i>Ini kali pertamaku melihat</i>

229
00:20:40,856 --> 00:20:43,442
<i>pria yang luar biasa.</i>

230
00:20:51,825 --> 00:20:52,826
<i>Aku tahu.</i>

231
00:20:53,244 --> 00:20:54,912
<i>Bau busuknya memudar.</i>

232
00:20:55,913 --> 00:20:57,665
<i>Aku bisa membedakan bau benangnya.</i>

233
00:20:58,499 --> 00:21:00,125
<i>Jika begini, aku bisa bertarung.</i>

234
00:21:02,628 --> 00:21:05,047
<i>Dia lebih cerdas dari dugaanku.</i>

235
00:21:05,756 --> 00:21:07,508
<i>Dia tak merasakan takut sama sekali.</i>

236
00:21:08,592 --> 00:21:11,387
<i>Tapi ini tak ada hubungannya
dengan kecerdasan.</i>

237
00:21:18,978 --> 00:21:20,396
<i>Napas Air.</i>

