00:21:20,813 --> 00:21:21,981
<i>Jurus Pertama.</i>

239
00:21:22,731 --> 00:21:24,692
<i>Tebasan Permukaan Air!</i>

240
00:23:03,163 --> 00:23:04,372
Hebat dan menakutkan!

241
00:23:04,456 --> 00:23:06,208
Kau mengalahkan iblis dalam sekejap!

242
00:23:06,291 --> 00:23:07,459
Siapa kau?

243
00:23:08,251 --> 00:23:11,171
Jurusmu sama seperti Monjiro.
Kalian berteman?

244
00:23:12,047 --> 00:23:13,340
Dia tak tahu aku di sini?

245
00:23:13,423 --> 00:23:14,758
Lihat aku!

246
00:23:14,966 --> 00:23:16,968
Ayo!

247
00:23:17,052 --> 00:23:18,220
Kau bisa melakukan ini?

248
00:23:19,137 --> 00:23:20,055
Hei!

249
00:23:22,724 --> 00:23:25,018
Biar kuberi tahu rahasia luar biasa.

250
00:23:25,102 --> 00:23:27,479
Tanjiro suka nasi kepal prem
dengan rumput laut.

251
00:23:27,562 --> 00:23:30,315
Zenitsu suka nasi kepal salmon.

252
00:23:31,775 --> 00:23:34,361
Berikutnya, episode 19, "Hinokami".

253
00:23:34,861 --> 00:23:36,363
Kau bisa bicara, ya!

254
